translation[8]{c,v,t}:
  29,31,"Aur jab hamare faristade (emissaries/messengers) Ibrahim ke paas basharat (khushkhabri) lekar pahunchey to unhon ne ussey kaha “hum is basti ke logon ko halaak karne waley hain, iske log sakht zaalim ho chuke hain.”"
  29,32,"Ibrahim ne kaha “wahan to Lut maujood hai”. Unhon ne kaha: “Hum khoob jantey hain ke wahan kaun kaun hai. Hum usey aur uski biwi ke siwa uske baaqi ghar waalon ko bacha lenge”. Uski biwi peechey reh janey walon mein se thi"
  29,33,"Phir jab hamare faristade (emissaries/messengers) Lut ke paas pahunchey to unki aamad par woh sakht pareshan aur dil tangg hua. Unhon ne kaha “ na daro aur na ranjh karo, hum tumhein aur tumhare ghar walon ko bacha lenge, siwaye tumhari biwi ke jo peechey reh janey walon mein se hai"
  29,34,Hum is basti ke logon par aasmaan se azaab nazil karne waley hain us fisq (evildoing) ke badaulat jo yeh karte rahey hain”
  29,35,Aur humne us basti ki ek khuli nishani chodh di hai un logon ke liye jo aqal se kaam letey hain
  29,36,"Aur Madyan ki taraf humne unke bhai Shoaib ko bheja.Usne kaha “Aey meri qaum ke logon, Allah ki bandagi karo aur roz e aakhir ke umeed-waar raho aur zameen mein mufsid ban kar zyadatiyan (mischief) na karte phiro”"
  29,37,Magar unhon ne usey jhutla diya. Aakhir e kaar ek sakht zalzaley ne unhein aa liya aur woh apne gharon mein padey ke padey reh gaye
  29,38,"Aur Aad o Samood ko humne halaak kiya, tum woh maqamaat dekh chuke ho jahan woh rehte thay. Unke aamal ko shaytaan ne unke liye khushnuma bana diya aur unhein raah e raast se bargashta kardiya, halanke woh hosh-gosh rakhte thay"